{"tid":2069243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貴格燕麥旗下品牌包裝涉種族歧視將撤換","createTime":"2020-06-18T08:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T16:43:21.000Z","uid":37554,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ff03b110c2a850cd3d7459ef45d774c92ff69c1f","tid":2069243,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:54:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國黑人弗洛伊德死亡案，令反種族歧視成為一股潮流。貴格燕麥旗下一個有逾130年歷史的品牌，包裝亦因為被指涉及種族歧視而被撤換，品牌亦要重新命名。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》報道，百事公司擁有的貴格燕麥，旗下有131年歷史的品牌「傑邁瑪阿姨」，產品以黑人女性畫像作為包裝，被指涉及種族歧視，公司在壓力下宣布換掉包裝設計並更改品牌名稱。<br />\n<br />\n1889年創立的「傑邁瑪阿姨」，主要售賣美式鬆餅粉、糖漿及其他早餐食品，是貴格燕麥旗下其中一個主要品牌。<br />\n<br />\n產品包裝上的黑人女子畫像，在1893年已開始使用，畫中人是品牌創辦人，根據一名黑奴形象繪畫，之後雖然曾多次更新，但仍一直被人質疑有種族歧視之嫌。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=394902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394902&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=ae6435d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394902&h=95613bfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=394902</a>"},{"pid":"7a3efb69bb721c786932e4154aa66b9109bcc9f4","tid":2069243,"uid":82532,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:55:17.000Z","msg":"黑人唔做得嘜頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"acaba466781426b6bbc61b89b870169ef915eb2e","tid":2069243,"uid":60109,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"黑人large size <br />\n係咪歧視中國人呀？"},{"pid":"48020bac478204c78cb7f7ed6630e8cabf7bffde","tid":2069243,"uid":194326,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ECzqOCCXYAA_NoZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FECzqOCCXYAA_NoZ.jpg&h=93d8ef92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid